T1  - Using Order Statistics to Estimate Real Estate Bid Distributions
AU  - Brown, Keith C.
AU  - Brown, Deborah J.
Y1  - 1986/03/01
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.32.3.289
